(thirdQuint)Study of Blood Samples From Patients With Ewing Sarcoma and Their Relatives.

 OBJECTIVES: - To identify and characterize a genetic susceptibility factor to Ewing's sarcoma by performing a Genome-Wide Association Study with as many as possible Ewing sarcoma patients.

 OUTLINE: This is a multicenter study.

 Blood samples are collected from patients and their relatives.

 Blood DNA samples are analyzed for susceptibility genes of Ewing Sarcoma.

